1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,020
♪ Inside the state a city is built ♪

2
00:00:05,020 --> 00:00:10,140
♪ Where a benevolent emperor resides ♪

3
00:00:10,140 --> 00:00:15,300
♪ Court officials are brave and able ♪

4
00:00:15,300 --> 00:00:22,700
♪ The empress is fair ♪

5
00:00:25,540 --> 00:00:30,660
♪ Princes died too young to ascend the throne ♪

6
00:00:30,660 --> 00:00:35,540
♪ Princesses are spoiled and fragile ♪

7
00:00:35,780 --> 00:00:40,220
♪ Commoners are also the emperor’s children ♪

8
00:00:40,780 --> 00:00:49,580
♪ All are living peacefully ♪

9
00:00:49,900 --> 00:00:54,220
♪ Wish I could live a day for myself ♪

10
00:00:54,940 --> 00:00:59,340
♪ Follow my heart and ethics without distractions ♪

11
00:01:00,660 --> 00:01:03,340
♪ To be a good husband ♪

12
00:01:03,340 --> 00:01:05,940
♪ To be a caring father ♪

13
00:01:06,420 --> 00:01:10,060
♪ We were close when we first met ♪

14
00:01:10,420 --> 00:01:14,660
♪ I hope I can control my desires ♪

15
00:01:15,500 --> 00:01:20,020
♪ To be a worriless emperor and father ♪

16
00:01:21,060 --> 00:01:23,820
♪ Prudence tops all virtues ♪

17
00:01:23,820 --> 00:01:26,420
♪ People build the state ♪

18
00:01:26,700 --> 00:01:30,020
= Held in the Lonely Castle =
♪ May the world be peaceful ♪

19
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:33,020
= Episode 41 =

20
00:02:03,420 --> 00:02:05,140
What is a flying cricket?

21
00:02:05,620 --> 00:02:07,340
It’s a kind of cricket

22
00:02:07,500 --> 00:02:08,380
with golden wings.

23
00:02:08,380 --> 00:02:09,380
It chirps most beautifully.

24
00:02:09,860 --> 00:02:10,660
Father. Father.

25
00:02:10,660 --> 00:02:11,820
I want to catch a flying cricket

26
00:02:11,820 --> 00:02:14,380
and have a look now.

27
00:02:25,540 --> 00:02:26,260
Your Majesty.

28
00:02:27,300 --> 00:02:29,580
Your maternal uncle has come with his two sons.

29
00:02:36,420 --> 00:02:37,820
Get them some tea.

30
00:02:38,140 --> 00:02:40,500
Get me an informal suit and crown.

31
00:02:41,620 --> 00:02:42,380
Yes, Your Majesty.

32
00:03:05,540 --> 00:03:06,220
Mother.

33
00:03:08,540 --> 00:03:09,940
I will be generous to your family.

34
00:03:11,900 --> 00:03:13,220
Whatever others argue,

35
00:03:14,540 --> 00:03:16,780
I will give your family the highest glory.

36
00:03:19,220 --> 00:03:20,580
Please bless Huirou

37
00:03:21,260 --> 00:03:23,500
and make her get better and recover.

38
00:03:26,220 --> 00:03:27,060
Mother.

39
00:03:29,140 --> 00:03:31,180
Zuixinglai has gone to heaven with you.

40
00:03:33,020 --> 00:03:34,260
Please bless Huirou.

41
00:03:35,940 --> 00:03:37,380
Please let me watch her grow up

42
00:03:38,020 --> 00:03:39,620
into a graceful girl

43
00:03:40,340 --> 00:03:41,220
and marry her to a man

44
00:03:43,020 --> 00:03:44,940
who spoils her like I do.

45
00:03:52,340 --> 00:03:55,100
= Li Zhang, courtesy name Gongming =

46
00:03:57,300 --> 00:03:58,020
His Majesty has arrived.

47
00:04:05,900 --> 00:04:06,900
Get up, uncle.

48
00:04:13,820 --> 00:04:14,540
Today,

49
00:04:17,500 --> 00:04:19,420
I ask you to come because I miss you.

50
00:04:19,980 --> 00:04:21,260
This is a family dinner.

51
00:04:21,300 --> 00:04:22,820
Make yourself at home.

52
00:04:23,940 --> 00:04:25,540
= Li Yonghe, courtesy name Shenli =
I can’t enjoy the family dinner

53
00:04:25,540 --> 00:04:26,660
until I report you

54
00:04:27,260 --> 00:04:28,980
public affairs.

55
00:04:30,380 --> 00:04:32,300
I was from a poor family.

56
00:04:33,540 --> 00:04:35,460
When I lived with Empress Dowager Zhangyi,

57
00:04:35,980 --> 00:04:37,300
she supported my study.

58
00:04:38,100 --> 00:04:39,020
After we lost touch,

59
00:04:39,580 --> 00:04:41,380
I did some odd jobs to make a living.

60
00:04:42,260 --> 00:04:45,100
I’m not smart or well-educated.

61
00:04:45,940 --> 00:04:47,620
But because my sister is Empress Dowager Zhangyi,

62
00:04:48,260 --> 00:04:49,860
I’m having such a high post

63
00:04:50,380 --> 00:04:51,500
and managing so many officials.

64
00:04:52,300 --> 00:04:53,500
I’m grateful,

65
00:04:54,220 --> 00:04:55,540
and I also fear I might let you down.

66
00:04:56,300 --> 00:04:57,780
What makes you think so?

67
00:04:58,660 --> 00:05:00,540
You’ve enjoyed a good reputation these years.

68
00:05:00,900 --> 00:05:02,180
Even if you don’t make great contribution,

69
00:05:02,380 --> 00:05:03,620
you’ve made no mistake, either.

70
00:05:04,100 --> 00:05:05,540
Why would you let me down?

71
00:05:06,260 --> 00:05:07,380
If most of the officials

72
00:05:07,740 --> 00:05:10,580
could be as careful and self-restrained as you,

73
00:05:10,860 --> 00:05:12,100
our nation would be in peace

74
00:05:12,100 --> 00:05:13,260
and people would live a happy life.

75
00:05:18,100 --> 00:05:19,020
In early years,

76
00:05:20,980 --> 00:05:22,180
I met

77
00:05:24,900 --> 00:05:26,260
my sister once.

78
00:05:30,420 --> 00:05:31,460
You met her?

79
00:05:33,100 --> 00:05:34,060
What did she say?

80
00:05:34,060 --> 00:05:36,580
Did...did she mention me?

81
00:05:37,900 --> 00:05:38,660
She said

82
00:05:40,620 --> 00:05:42,340
we should have been

83
00:05:43,340 --> 00:05:47,620
common people like farmers or traders.

84
00:05:49,380 --> 00:05:50,820
By chance,

85
00:05:51,860 --> 00:05:53,380
we became the relatives of the Emperor.

86
00:05:55,500 --> 00:05:57,060
She said Your Majesty had filial piety

87
00:05:58,180 --> 00:05:59,980
and you would certainly take care of us.

88
00:06:01,620 --> 00:06:03,460
Yet we couldn’t help you much.

89
00:06:03,900 --> 00:06:07,660
Then we should just try not to

90
00:06:10,780 --> 00:06:12,020
make troubles for you.

91
00:06:15,220 --> 00:06:16,740
I’m always an ordinary man.

92
00:06:18,100 --> 00:06:19,700
Now, I’m nearly sixty.

93
00:06:20,340 --> 00:06:21,420
I’m too old and sick

94
00:06:22,140 --> 00:06:23,420
to bear important tasks.

95
00:06:24,700 --> 00:06:26,220
Your Majesty, if you care for me,

96
00:06:27,180 --> 00:06:29,420
please approve of my retirement.

97
00:06:45,060 --> 00:06:45,940
Get up.

98
00:06:51,660 --> 00:06:52,580
Get up.

99
00:07:04,620 --> 00:07:05,340
Prime Minister Yan.

100
00:07:10,180 --> 00:07:12,940
Since the four nestlings were born,

101
00:07:13,700 --> 00:07:16,220
the swallow parents have been busy around.

102
00:07:17,180 --> 00:07:18,380
In the storm yesterday,

103
00:07:19,300 --> 00:07:22,140
the male swallow didn’t stop

104
00:07:22,580 --> 00:07:23,940
even when its wings were broken.

105
00:07:25,020 --> 00:07:27,540
The love between parents and children

106
00:07:29,100 --> 00:07:31,180
never changes in this world.

107
00:07:32,860 --> 00:07:35,340
It’s the hardest to suffer

108
00:07:36,660 --> 00:07:37,580
when a young man loses his parents

109
00:07:37,580 --> 00:07:39,380
or middle-aged parents lose their children.

110
00:07:42,580 --> 00:07:43,660
The Eighth Prince is badly ill,

111
00:07:44,140 --> 00:07:46,300
and specially allowed to recuperate in the palace.

112
00:07:46,980 --> 00:07:48,900
His Majesty stops working and eats less for days

113
00:07:49,660 --> 00:07:50,900
to pray for him.

114
00:07:51,900 --> 00:07:54,460
His Majesty cares a lot for his family.

115
00:07:57,780 --> 00:07:59,140
Is the Eighth Prince getting better?

116
00:08:00,460 --> 00:08:02,180
He’s getting worse.

117
00:08:02,660 --> 00:08:03,940
He can’t even recognize people.

118
00:08:05,140 --> 00:08:07,580
His Majesty and Her Highness donated 5,000 copper

119
00:08:07,740 --> 00:08:10,260
to set medicine sheds and congee sheds
in the Capital

120
00:08:10,380 --> 00:08:11,660
to pray for the royal family.

121
00:08:13,580 --> 00:08:14,820
I come here,

122
00:08:15,820 --> 00:08:17,420
with the autograph edict of His Majesty.

123
00:08:17,700 --> 00:08:19,180
Please kindly read.

124
00:08:25,660 --> 00:08:26,980
Oh, I’ve got something else

125
00:08:32,300 --> 00:08:34,300
to ask you for a favor.

126
00:08:36,340 --> 00:08:38,580
Come on. Wei. Have some more.

127
00:08:39,500 --> 00:08:40,180
Here.

128
00:08:45,980 --> 00:08:46,980
Behave yourself.

129
00:08:58,540 --> 00:09:01,380
He’s just like what he was in the childhood.

130
00:09:02,180 --> 00:09:03,500
He reminds me of the old days

131
00:09:03,740 --> 00:09:04,940
when he carried Huirou

132
00:09:04,940 --> 00:09:06,380
to fetch the candied fruits.

133
00:09:08,060 --> 00:09:09,260
Thanks to you, young master.

134
00:09:09,700 --> 00:09:12,260
It’s been days since His Majesty smiled

135
00:09:14,180 --> 00:09:15,460
when he kept worrying about state affairs and...

136
00:09:15,700 --> 00:09:17,060
And the illness of the Eighth Prince.

137
00:09:20,580 --> 00:09:21,420
Uncle.

138
00:09:22,340 --> 00:09:24,380
You said all the families had imperial favor

139
00:09:24,380 --> 00:09:25,380
and got promoted.

140
00:09:25,380 --> 00:09:26,660
But you forget Wei.

141
00:09:28,780 --> 00:09:29,940
He is only twelve.

142
00:09:30,420 --> 00:09:32,260
He’s much more stupid

143
00:09:32,460 --> 00:09:33,380
than his brother at his age.

144
00:09:34,100 --> 00:09:36,580
His mother was from a poor family

145
00:09:36,900 --> 00:09:38,140
who didn’t even read.

146
00:09:38,700 --> 00:09:39,980
After having him,

147
00:09:40,260 --> 00:09:41,380
we became rich.

148
00:09:41,700 --> 00:09:43,260
He’s a spoilt boy.

149
00:09:44,660 --> 00:09:46,900
I don’t quite agree, uncle.

150
00:09:47,900 --> 00:09:48,700
He shares

151
00:09:48,700 --> 00:09:50,300
half the blood as I do.

152
00:09:50,460 --> 00:09:51,620
Why is he stupid?

153
00:09:52,420 --> 00:09:53,740
I think he’s a very good boy.

154
00:09:54,300 --> 00:09:55,300
He is simple and honest,

155
00:09:55,660 --> 00:09:56,700
unlike those showy boys

156
00:09:56,700 --> 00:09:58,540
from official families.

157
00:09:59,340 --> 00:10:01,420
I… I think...

158
00:10:03,860 --> 00:10:05,540
His mother and I fail to teach him well.

159
00:10:05,820 --> 00:10:06,660
After we go back home,

160
00:10:07,060 --> 00:10:08,660
we will instruct him

161
00:10:09,220 --> 00:10:10,500
and won’t let you down.

162
00:10:11,060 --> 00:10:14,100
But we don’t dare to make him an official.

163
00:10:14,500 --> 00:10:15,620
Even if it’s a nominal title,

164
00:10:16,220 --> 00:10:18,060
he’s too young

165
00:10:18,460 --> 00:10:19,460
to accept it.

166
00:10:19,580 --> 00:10:20,820
He can’t accept it.

167
00:10:24,260 --> 00:10:25,620
He is young.

168
00:10:26,460 --> 00:10:29,140
If he has a title and pay,

169
00:10:29,580 --> 00:10:30,540
I’m afraid he’ll be lazy

170
00:10:30,660 --> 00:10:31,780
and idle the days away.

171
00:10:33,620 --> 00:10:35,940
But even if you don’t want a title,

172
00:10:36,180 --> 00:10:37,340
I shall also award you.

173
00:10:38,540 --> 00:10:40,260
Tell me what you want.

174
00:10:42,700 --> 00:10:43,860
Don’t look at your father.

175
00:10:44,260 --> 00:10:45,700
I call the shots here.

176
00:10:48,420 --> 00:10:49,220
Whatever I want?

177
00:10:50,900 --> 00:10:52,700
Why don’t you tell me first?

178
00:10:53,860 --> 00:10:55,900
Your Majesty,

179
00:10:55,900 --> 00:10:57,460
I want to see Huirou again.

180
00:10:57,940 --> 00:10:59,380
She loves candied fruits.

181
00:10:59,980 --> 00:11:01,980
Later, I found

182
00:11:01,980 --> 00:11:03,140
many kinds of them

183
00:11:03,340 --> 00:11:04,340
in different places.

184
00:11:04,580 --> 00:11:05,580
They taste great.

185
00:11:05,940 --> 00:11:07,620
Some are even better than those in the palace.

186
00:11:08,700 --> 00:11:10,700
In the imperial banquet every year,

187
00:11:10,900 --> 00:11:11,860
I...

188
00:11:13,980 --> 00:11:16,540
I brought many candied fruits and snacks

189
00:11:16,860 --> 00:11:18,500
to the palace

190
00:11:18,860 --> 00:11:20,100
for Huirou.

191
00:11:20,660 --> 00:11:22,860
But she always followed

192
00:11:22,860 --> 00:11:23,900
Her Highness

193
00:11:24,300 --> 00:11:25,700
and sat far away from me.

194
00:11:26,020 --> 00:11:27,420
I didn’t dare to talk to her,

195
00:11:27,780 --> 00:11:28,820
in case my father might beat me.

196
00:11:31,580 --> 00:11:32,660
They are apricot sweets,

197
00:11:32,780 --> 00:11:34,460
made of secret recipe from Winehouse Fan.

198
00:11:34,740 --> 00:11:36,260
Only a few pots are available for sell every year.

199
00:11:36,580 --> 00:11:37,900
I waited before daybreak

200
00:11:37,900 --> 00:11:38,620
and finally bought them.

201
00:11:38,900 --> 00:11:40,020
Huirou will love them.

202
00:11:40,700 --> 00:11:43,540
May I go to the backyard

203
00:11:44,060 --> 00:11:47,620
and...and give them to Huirou?

204
00:11:54,620 --> 00:11:55,580
Sorry, Your Majesty.

205
00:11:55,980 --> 00:11:56,900
He’s a naughty boy

206
00:11:57,460 --> 00:11:59,140
and doesn’t know imperial rules.

207
00:11:59,860 --> 00:12:00,740
Please forgive him, Your Majesty.

208
00:12:00,940 --> 00:12:04,140
No. Please punish him.

209
00:12:04,380 --> 00:12:05,380
Punish him severely.

210
00:12:09,260 --> 00:12:09,980
It’s okay.

211
00:12:11,020 --> 00:12:11,940
Get up.

212
00:12:12,500 --> 00:12:13,380
Get up.

213
00:12:20,860 --> 00:12:21,700
I can’t go?

214
00:12:22,780 --> 00:12:24,980
But…but...

215
00:12:25,500 --> 00:12:26,940
They are great candied fruits.

216
00:12:27,140 --> 00:12:28,300
They can’t be found in the palace.

217
00:12:28,580 --> 00:12:29,980
Secret recipe from Winehouse Fan.

218
00:12:31,660 --> 00:12:32,340
Come.

219
00:12:41,700 --> 00:12:44,220
I asked you to name something you want.

220
00:12:44,380 --> 00:12:46,620
But you asked to

221
00:12:46,780 --> 00:12:47,580
exchange the award

222
00:12:47,860 --> 00:12:50,100
with a chance to give Huirou the candied fruits.

223
00:12:52,380 --> 00:12:53,220
Why?

224
00:12:53,660 --> 00:12:55,260
Because Huirou loves candied fruits.

225
00:12:55,300 --> 00:12:56,180
I still remember.

226
00:12:59,860 --> 00:13:01,820
You think he goes beyond imperial rules.

227
00:13:02,180 --> 00:13:05,580
But I think

228
00:13:06,140 --> 00:13:07,380
it’s such imperial rules that

229
00:13:07,380 --> 00:13:08,660
stop the true nature.

230
00:13:11,020 --> 00:13:11,980
My daughter Huirou

231
00:13:12,380 --> 00:13:14,540
is the most honorable girl in our nation.

232
00:13:14,900 --> 00:13:16,020
She receives everything,

233
00:13:16,620 --> 00:13:17,700
only except

234
00:13:18,060 --> 00:13:21,140
such true nature of common people.

235
00:13:23,500 --> 00:13:25,620
I’ll take the candied fruits for her.

236
00:13:27,100 --> 00:13:28,100
She has a cold

237
00:13:28,300 --> 00:13:29,660
and she can’t meet any guest today.

238
00:13:29,980 --> 00:13:31,180
But I promise you.

239
00:13:31,300 --> 00:13:32,220
At this year’s banquet,

240
00:13:32,380 --> 00:13:34,140
I’ll make you sit with Huirou.

241
00:13:34,740 --> 00:13:36,820
If you have new snacks,

242
00:13:37,300 --> 00:13:38,420
you can give them to her personally.

243
00:13:40,460 --> 00:13:41,700
Say thank you to His Majesty.

244
00:13:45,140 --> 00:13:46,860
= Shi Mansion =
Aren’t those guys

245
00:13:47,220 --> 00:13:48,140
sent by the government

246
00:13:48,140 --> 00:13:49,140
to stop Shi Jie from defecting?

247
00:13:49,980 --> 00:13:51,580
Why are they caught by Imperial Security Agency?

248
00:13:52,100 --> 00:13:54,020
I hear they are fake guards.

249
00:13:55,100 --> 00:13:56,140
Go. Hurry.

250
00:13:56,140 --> 00:13:57,740
- What’s wrong with squatting here?
- Then is Shi Jie a real traitor?

251
00:13:57,740 --> 00:13:58,900
- I’m not doing any crime. - Go.

252
00:13:58,900 --> 00:14:00,020
Why can you arrest me?

253
00:14:00,020 --> 00:14:01,140
Go. Stop yelling.

254
00:14:01,260 --> 00:14:03,020
We’re taking you to Kaifeng Municipal Government.

255
00:14:03,020 --> 00:14:04,140
Why do you think you can?

256
00:14:04,740 --> 00:14:05,420
Look at you.

257
00:14:05,420 --> 00:14:05,860
Hurry!

258
00:14:05,860 --> 00:14:07,060
You wear our uniforms without permission.

259
00:14:07,060 --> 00:14:07,820
Go!

260
00:14:08,540 --> 00:14:10,500
They’re rogues?

261
00:14:10,500 --> 00:14:11,140
Hurry up!

262
00:14:12,940 --> 00:14:14,340
- I don’t think Mr. Shi - Hurry!

263
00:14:14,380 --> 00:14:16,060
is a real traitor.

264
00:14:16,500 --> 00:14:17,900
Why didn’t he tell on them?

265
00:14:18,700 --> 00:14:19,580
- No idea. - Hurry!

266
00:14:19,900 --> 00:14:20,660
Go. Go.

267
00:14:27,860 --> 00:14:31,260
= Shi Jie, courtesy name Shoudao =

268
00:14:43,740 --> 00:14:44,580
Mr. Shi.

269
00:14:49,420 --> 00:14:50,460
There you are.

270
00:14:52,180 --> 00:14:54,420
Finally, you’re here.

271
00:15:14,940 --> 00:15:16,820
Give me a few minutes.

272
00:15:17,780 --> 00:15:19,220
I’ll go with you

273
00:15:19,340 --> 00:15:21,180
after I get washed and changed.

274
00:15:22,300 --> 00:15:23,540
I’m a scholar.

275
00:15:24,260 --> 00:15:26,620
I must keep myself clean.

276
00:15:31,580 --> 00:15:33,940
I dare not to get you out, Mr. Shi.

277
00:15:34,740 --> 00:15:37,060
I just come to tell you that

278
00:15:38,060 --> 00:15:38,980
I’ve sent away

279
00:15:38,980 --> 00:15:40,820
those rogues outside your house

280
00:15:41,340 --> 00:15:43,220
who pretend to be with Imperial Security Agency.

281
00:15:45,820 --> 00:15:47,180
Pretend?

282
00:15:48,700 --> 00:15:49,540
Rogues?

283
00:15:52,460 --> 00:15:54,420
I asked guards from Imperial Security Agency

284
00:15:54,460 --> 00:15:55,700
to arrest them and send them to

285
00:15:56,220 --> 00:15:57,940
Kaifeng Municipal Government.

286
00:15:58,860 --> 00:16:01,260
I come in to tell you that

287
00:16:01,820 --> 00:16:03,620
if anyone else dares to come

288
00:16:03,740 --> 00:16:04,780
and makes trouble for you,

289
00:16:05,180 --> 00:16:07,980
you can send me a message.

290
00:16:12,900 --> 00:16:14,020
Please stay.

291
00:16:18,820 --> 00:16:20,340
I rethink again and again.

292
00:16:20,580 --> 00:16:22,580
I think I’m too stupid

293
00:16:22,580 --> 00:16:24,060
to be an important official.

294
00:16:24,300 --> 00:16:25,060
I’ve submitted seventeen proposals

295
00:16:25,060 --> 00:16:26,820
to ask for punishment.

296
00:16:27,180 --> 00:16:30,140
But I never want to betray His Majesty.

297
00:16:30,860 --> 00:16:32,380
I wrote the Ode

298
00:16:32,620 --> 00:16:34,340
to praise His Majesty

299
00:16:34,540 --> 00:16:36,020
and admire those noble officials

300
00:16:36,100 --> 00:16:37,220
from the bottom of my heart.

301
00:16:37,540 --> 00:16:38,900
Even if I could go back to the past,

302
00:16:38,900 --> 00:16:40,100
I would still write that

303
00:16:40,100 --> 00:16:40,980
without any modification.

304
00:16:41,820 --> 00:16:42,660
But…

305
00:16:43,340 --> 00:16:46,060
I only admire those gentlemen.

306
00:16:46,060 --> 00:16:47,580
I don’t even make friends with them.

307
00:16:47,580 --> 00:16:49,260
Not to mention ganging up.

308
00:16:49,700 --> 00:16:51,740
If I’m too stupid to work,

309
00:16:51,820 --> 00:16:53,420
I can quit the job.

310
00:16:53,900 --> 00:16:55,780
But if I’m accused of

311
00:16:55,780 --> 00:16:57,580
ganging up and betraying the nation,

312
00:16:58,100 --> 00:16:59,740
I’d rather be tortured to death

313
00:16:59,780 --> 00:17:02,020
than be framed up.

314
00:17:03,820 --> 00:17:05,100
You’re an honest and frank man.

315
00:17:05,420 --> 00:17:06,780
I always admire you.

316
00:17:08,100 --> 00:17:10,420
In fact, Mr. Yan asked me

317
00:17:11,300 --> 00:17:12,380
to tell you something.

318
00:17:13,340 --> 00:17:15,100
Being too stubborn will get you hurt.

319
00:17:18,540 --> 00:17:19,820
Mr. Shi, you’re a very learned man.

320
00:17:20,340 --> 00:17:22,700
Even if you can’t work for the imperial court,

321
00:17:23,540 --> 00:17:26,780
you can still instruct students

322
00:17:27,260 --> 00:17:30,140
and pass down your knowledge for centuries.

323
00:17:55,420 --> 00:17:57,700
Zhang Maoze helped Shi Jie.

324
00:18:10,140 --> 00:18:12,100
Could His Majesty send him?

325
00:18:15,620 --> 00:18:16,700
After news came out that

326
00:18:16,700 --> 00:18:18,620
Shi Jie wrote the letters for treason

327
00:18:18,620 --> 00:18:19,580
by himself,

328
00:18:21,140 --> 00:18:23,300
Fu Bi asked to leave the Capital immediately.

329
00:18:24,820 --> 00:18:28,220
Even Ouyang Xiu,

330
00:18:28,220 --> 00:18:31,420
who claimed to be his friend

331
00:18:33,700 --> 00:18:37,660
didn’t dare to defend Shi Jie

332
00:18:37,660 --> 00:18:39,060
in case he might be accused of treason too.

333
00:18:53,580 --> 00:18:55,220
Could His Majesty change his mind

334
00:18:56,980 --> 00:18:58,300
because Zuixinglai gets better?

335
00:19:13,420 --> 00:19:14,220
Mr. Zhang.

336
00:19:15,180 --> 00:19:16,780
You work in the imperial court, huh?

337
00:19:17,580 --> 00:19:19,500
With Privy Council or Imperial Academy?

338
00:19:20,780 --> 00:19:22,060
For your information,

339
00:19:22,540 --> 00:19:24,700
I used to work with Imperial Academy.

340
00:19:25,140 --> 00:19:27,580
Later I was transferred to Privy Council.

341
00:19:28,580 --> 00:19:29,820
Why do you come here?

342
00:19:30,660 --> 00:19:32,380
= Zhang Chengzhao =

343
00:19:32,380 --> 00:19:33,100
Uh...

344
00:19:37,260 --> 00:19:39,180
Liang Huaiji

345
00:19:39,180 --> 00:19:40,540
who lived with me

346
00:19:40,540 --> 00:19:41,660
was transferred to imperial harem

347
00:19:42,460 --> 00:19:43,780
and didn’t come back for days.

348
00:19:44,580 --> 00:19:46,660
He asked me to send something to him.

349
00:19:58,340 --> 00:19:59,620
Zhang Chengzhao?

350
00:20:00,860 --> 00:20:03,100
Cheng for connection and Zhao for sunlight.

351
00:20:04,300 --> 00:20:06,340
Chief Xia recommended you to Privy Council.

352
00:20:09,620 --> 00:20:10,460
Aye.

353
00:20:13,900 --> 00:20:16,660
It’s too late. Get back soon.

354
00:20:32,940 --> 00:20:34,500
Road in the palace are complicated.

355
00:20:35,820 --> 00:20:37,180
You think you’re familiar.

356
00:20:37,940 --> 00:20:41,140
But you’ll even

357
00:20:41,540 --> 00:20:42,420
get killed

358
00:20:43,300 --> 00:20:44,100
if you walk the wrong way.

359
00:20:49,180 --> 00:20:50,660
Take this lamp.

360
00:20:51,180 --> 00:20:52,260
It helps to light your way.

361
00:20:53,420 --> 00:20:54,180
But...

362
00:20:55,340 --> 00:20:58,460
you’d better not go anywhere

363
00:20:58,460 --> 00:20:59,740
you shouldn’t go.

364
00:21:26,900 --> 00:21:31,740
= Records of Recruitment =

365
00:21:34,940 --> 00:21:36,020
Lantiao?

366
00:21:38,140 --> 00:21:39,860
Aunt Jia trusts her so much.

367
00:21:40,900 --> 00:21:41,780
That makes no sense.

368
00:21:58,700 --> 00:21:59,460
Your Highness.

369
00:22:00,180 --> 00:22:01,900
Miss Dong asked me

370
00:22:01,900 --> 00:22:04,060
to serve you.

371
00:22:07,620 --> 00:22:08,420
Where is she?

372
00:22:09,820 --> 00:22:11,580
His Majesty just asked

373
00:22:12,020 --> 00:22:14,620
Chief of Styling Gu to comb his hair.

374
00:22:15,220 --> 00:22:17,180
But she had the pestilence.

375
00:22:17,900 --> 00:22:18,740
She has recovered,

376
00:22:18,900 --> 00:22:20,460
but she isn’t as healthy as before.

377
00:22:21,020 --> 00:22:22,620
Miss Dong went to the Hall
of Happiness and Tranquility

378
00:22:23,020 --> 00:22:24,540
and asked me to take care of you.

379
00:22:35,460 --> 00:22:37,340
His Majesty summoned Qiuhe?

380
00:22:39,740 --> 00:22:40,340
Yes.

381
00:22:40,500 --> 00:22:42,980
She asked me to take care of you, Your Highness.

382
00:23:21,100 --> 00:23:22,420
Your Majesty, please forgive me

383
00:23:22,900 --> 00:23:23,940
for coming without telling you.

384
00:23:27,540 --> 00:23:28,300
There you are.

385
00:23:33,220 --> 00:23:34,420
I have something

386
00:23:34,820 --> 00:23:35,940
to discuss with you.

387
00:23:39,740 --> 00:23:40,500
What is it?

388
00:23:48,940 --> 00:23:51,940
= Dong Qiuhe =

389
00:23:52,340 --> 00:23:54,620
Chief of Styling Gu Cai’er

390
00:23:54,860 --> 00:23:56,380
was ill, too.

391
00:23:57,980 --> 00:23:59,580
She’s getting better.

392
00:23:59,820 --> 00:24:00,940
But the physician said

393
00:24:01,100 --> 00:24:02,980
she was so badly sick

394
00:24:03,260 --> 00:24:04,980
that it would take her months to recover.

395
00:24:06,140 --> 00:24:07,220
I’m afraid

396
00:24:08,300 --> 00:24:09,580
she can’t be the chief anymore.

397
00:24:10,700 --> 00:24:12,020
So, I think...

398
00:24:23,620 --> 00:24:25,220
stewardess Hu Yuewei

399
00:24:26,100 --> 00:24:27,140
is 21 years old.

400
00:24:27,540 --> 00:24:29,900
She is mild and decorous.

401
00:24:30,300 --> 00:24:31,580
She came to the palace
at the age of seven or eight.

402
00:24:31,860 --> 00:24:33,420
And she is familiar with imperial rules.

403
00:24:34,220 --> 00:24:35,980
Before she is a tailor,

404
00:24:36,220 --> 00:24:38,100
she worked as a stylist for four years

405
00:24:38,140 --> 00:24:39,900
and she’s good at guiding technique.

406
00:24:42,540 --> 00:24:43,780
Shall I send her to you

407
00:24:44,140 --> 00:24:45,380
tomorrow morning

408
00:24:45,820 --> 00:24:47,940
and try combing your hair?

409
00:24:48,940 --> 00:24:50,340
If you feel satisfied,

410
00:24:50,940 --> 00:24:52,180
promote her as the chief.

411
00:24:57,300 --> 00:24:58,100
Your Majesty.

412
00:25:01,700 --> 00:25:03,100
What do you think?

413
00:25:04,420 --> 00:25:06,100
Her Highness went to the Hall
of Happiness and Tranquility.

414
00:25:06,700 --> 00:25:08,020
Weren’t you combing the hair for His Majesty

415
00:25:08,020 --> 00:25:09,300
in the Hall of Happiness and Tranquility?

416
00:25:09,700 --> 00:25:10,460
You didn’t see her?

417
00:25:11,140 --> 00:25:13,060
Xiaowu came?

418
00:25:13,740 --> 00:25:16,140
She told Her Highness I was summoned,

419
00:25:16,500 --> 00:25:17,860
and then Her Highness went there?

420
00:25:18,420 --> 00:25:20,740
Yes. Xiaowu did come.

421
00:25:20,820 --> 00:25:21,780
After that, Her Highness left

422
00:25:21,780 --> 00:25:23,060
for the Hall of Happiness and Tranquility.

423
00:25:27,580 --> 00:25:28,620
I’m too stupid.

424
00:25:29,500 --> 00:25:30,860
I only care for myself.

425
00:25:31,740 --> 00:25:33,340
Thinking Her Highness always keeps her promise,

426
00:25:33,460 --> 00:25:35,580
I… I fancied myself clever.

427
00:25:35,580 --> 00:25:36,660
I’m so sorry.

428
00:25:42,900 --> 00:25:43,740
What a coincidence!

429
00:25:44,780 --> 00:25:47,260
I just asked Dong Qiuhe

430
00:25:47,260 --> 00:25:48,420
to comb my hair

431
00:25:48,620 --> 00:25:49,500
and massage me.

432
00:25:50,500 --> 00:25:51,580
I think

433
00:25:52,300 --> 00:25:54,060
Dong Qiuhe does a much better job

434
00:25:54,340 --> 00:25:55,900
than Gu Cai’er.

435
00:25:56,300 --> 00:25:57,460
She’s clever and sensible.

436
00:25:58,740 --> 00:26:01,220
Is Hu Yuewei better than her?

437
00:26:04,820 --> 00:26:06,420
Qiuhe is smart.

438
00:26:09,100 --> 00:26:11,140
But she’s too young.

439
00:26:12,620 --> 00:26:14,740
If we make her the Chief of Styling,

440
00:26:15,620 --> 00:26:16,620
even if she’s capable enough

441
00:26:16,620 --> 00:26:17,980
to take charge of a branch,

442
00:26:18,940 --> 00:26:20,540
others may not be convinced.

443
00:26:24,580 --> 00:26:27,100
Is that what you truly mean?

444
00:26:32,500 --> 00:26:33,900
You don’t want

445
00:26:33,900 --> 00:26:36,020
Dong Qiuhe to take the place of Gu Cai’er

446
00:26:36,460 --> 00:26:38,500
because she will then

447
00:26:38,500 --> 00:26:39,860
take care of my daily living?

448
00:26:41,500 --> 00:26:42,940
Or are you worried about

449
00:26:43,140 --> 00:26:44,580
her moral character

450
00:26:46,180 --> 00:26:48,180
and thinking she wants to seduce me

451
00:26:48,340 --> 00:26:50,300
at such a young age?

452
00:26:50,300 --> 00:26:50,980
No.

453
00:26:51,820 --> 00:26:52,900
Qiuhe is a good girl.

454
00:26:54,740 --> 00:26:56,380
She’s clever, sensible,

455
00:26:56,700 --> 00:26:57,860
and loyal.

456
00:26:59,700 --> 00:27:01,140
Since she’s so good

457
00:27:01,340 --> 00:27:03,660
and capable,

458
00:27:04,340 --> 00:27:05,780
and she’s already a stylist,

459
00:27:06,740 --> 00:27:09,100
why do you want to transfer another girl

460
00:27:09,100 --> 00:27:10,820
instead of promoting her directly?

461
00:27:11,340 --> 00:27:12,180
Or…

462
00:27:13,460 --> 00:27:15,260
you don’t want her to stay with me?

463
00:27:16,940 --> 00:27:18,780
Do you do this,

464
00:27:19,220 --> 00:27:20,180
for me,

465
00:27:21,420 --> 00:27:22,540
or for her?

466
00:27:27,860 --> 00:27:29,260
Why don’t you answer me?

467
00:27:31,300 --> 00:27:32,580
You do not want to tell the truth

468
00:27:33,980 --> 00:27:35,460
or lie?

469
00:27:44,500 --> 00:27:45,340
Forget it.

470
00:27:47,660 --> 00:27:48,900
Cheating me is a capital offence.

471
00:27:50,500 --> 00:27:52,100
I won’t force you.

472
00:27:52,860 --> 00:27:54,180
So, I’m not asking anymore.

473
00:27:57,900 --> 00:27:58,900
Since you think

474
00:27:58,900 --> 00:28:00,820
Dong Qiuhe is too young to be the chief.

475
00:28:01,540 --> 00:28:03,820
I will assign someone,

476
00:28:03,820 --> 00:28:04,660
who is old enough

477
00:28:05,020 --> 00:28:06,460
and does a good job of combing

478
00:28:06,900 --> 00:28:08,500
and whom I’m familiar with.

479
00:28:09,700 --> 00:28:11,940
Maid Xu Lantiao of the Pavilion of Luan.

480
00:28:13,620 --> 00:28:14,780
No more argument.

481
00:28:46,900 --> 00:28:47,700
Your Highness.

482
00:28:52,660 --> 00:28:53,460
Don’t worry.

483
00:28:55,020 --> 00:28:56,420
His Majesty promised me

484
00:28:56,900 --> 00:28:58,220
not to promote you.

485
00:29:00,300 --> 00:29:01,220
But...

486
00:29:03,140 --> 00:29:04,660
He’s already suspecting.

487
00:29:05,420 --> 00:29:06,580
I can’t let you out

488
00:29:07,220 --> 00:29:08,500
in a short time.

489
00:29:10,100 --> 00:29:13,700
It’s hard to predict what His Majesty thinks.

490
00:29:14,180 --> 00:29:15,020
I can’t risk letting His Majesty,

491
00:29:15,780 --> 00:29:17,860
Officer Ren or Deputy Officer Yang suspect

492
00:29:18,420 --> 00:29:19,900
that you are in a relationship
with someone outside

493
00:29:20,340 --> 00:29:22,140
when you worked here.

494
00:29:24,140 --> 00:29:26,180
This is a great taboo.

495
00:29:29,740 --> 00:29:30,580
Your Highness.

496
00:29:31,180 --> 00:29:33,780
I made a mistake because I was too bumptious.

497
00:29:34,740 --> 00:29:36,100
What’s done can’t be undone.

498
00:29:36,700 --> 00:29:39,100
But I must do one thing in the future.

499
00:29:40,100 --> 00:29:43,180
I’ll stay with you and take care of you.

500
00:29:47,740 --> 00:29:51,260
This is a decree.

501
00:29:54,060 --> 00:29:55,180
A decree?

502
00:29:56,900 --> 00:29:59,020
Today, His Majesty summoned me

503
00:30:00,220 --> 00:30:01,700
for you, Your Highness.

504
00:30:02,820 --> 00:30:04,700
He noticed what you’ve done

505
00:30:04,940 --> 00:30:06,500
in recent days.

506
00:30:07,300 --> 00:30:08,860
He summoned me

507
00:30:09,540 --> 00:30:11,820
and asked if you were getting better

508
00:30:12,260 --> 00:30:13,460
and what medicine you were taking.

509
00:30:14,820 --> 00:30:15,700
His Majesty said

510
00:30:16,260 --> 00:30:17,420
considering your temper,

511
00:30:17,620 --> 00:30:18,980
you need a careful maid

512
00:30:18,980 --> 00:30:21,340
to take care of you

513
00:30:21,340 --> 00:30:22,500
and relieve you.

514
00:30:23,180 --> 00:30:25,940
So, he transferred me to the Hall of Peace

515
00:30:26,500 --> 00:30:28,780
and stay with you.

516
00:30:29,020 --> 00:30:30,620
I’ll take care of your daily living

517
00:30:31,020 --> 00:30:33,180
in the name of a Chief of Styling.

518
00:30:38,460 --> 00:30:42,180
Your Highness, His Majesty cares for you.

519
00:30:43,740 --> 00:30:44,820
He said

520
00:30:45,380 --> 00:30:46,900
when you accompanied his children

521
00:30:46,900 --> 00:30:48,460
for him,

522
00:30:49,700 --> 00:30:51,900
you not only risked your own health,

523
00:30:52,860 --> 00:30:54,900
but also borne great responsibilities.

524
00:30:56,500 --> 00:30:57,300
Now...

525
00:30:59,660 --> 00:31:03,540
Now the prince is dead.

526
00:31:05,140 --> 00:31:06,940
Madam Miao is the saddest.

527
00:31:07,780 --> 00:31:09,940
But you’re the most embarrassed.

528
00:31:11,340 --> 00:31:14,580
His Majesty said the prince was dead,

529
00:31:15,660 --> 00:31:17,460
but he must protect Madam Miao

530
00:31:18,060 --> 00:31:19,220
and he must protect you.

531
00:31:22,660 --> 00:31:23,580
Protect?

532
00:31:27,580 --> 00:31:29,460
Your Highness. It’s my fault.

533
00:31:29,700 --> 00:31:32,340
I fancied myself clever

534
00:31:32,460 --> 00:31:34,140
and made you misunderstand His Majesty.

535
00:31:41,820 --> 00:31:43,340
If I trusted him,

536
00:31:47,700 --> 00:31:49,100
why could I ever misunderstand him?

537
00:31:54,540 --> 00:31:56,180
He blames me for not trusting him.

538
00:31:58,340 --> 00:31:59,740
But he has no idea that

539
00:32:01,780 --> 00:32:05,060
I believe his morality.

540
00:32:09,500 --> 00:32:11,580
I just don’t believe he loves me.

541
00:32:11,860 --> 00:32:12,980
So, I hold grudges.

542
00:32:16,980 --> 00:32:18,820
Because of this,

543
00:32:20,620 --> 00:32:22,100
I suspect him and guard against him.

544
00:32:25,900 --> 00:32:26,740
Qiuhe.

545
00:32:29,380 --> 00:32:30,900
I’m too narrow-minded.

546
00:32:32,300 --> 00:32:33,540
It’s not your fault.

547
00:32:42,220 --> 00:32:42,980
Shoudao.

548
00:32:43,660 --> 00:32:45,100
When you were wronged,

549
00:32:46,980 --> 00:32:49,700
for the so-called overall situation,

550
00:32:51,180 --> 00:32:53,020
we only protected ourselves.

551
00:32:53,020 --> 00:32:54,940
None of us defended you.

552
00:32:57,700 --> 00:33:00,380
I thought you would only be banished

553
00:33:00,620 --> 00:33:01,820
and the truth would be cleared

554
00:33:02,980 --> 00:33:04,700
in two or three years.

555
00:33:05,180 --> 00:33:06,860
= Grave of Shi Jie =

556
00:33:06,860 --> 00:33:07,940
Unexpectedly,

557
00:33:10,780 --> 00:33:11,980
you had a relapse and died

558
00:33:14,180 --> 00:33:15,740
even before you left the Capital.

559
00:33:27,260 --> 00:33:28,300
I still remember

560
00:33:30,500 --> 00:33:32,860
how proud you were when you wrote the Ode.

561
00:33:34,580 --> 00:33:37,380
At that time, Fan Zhongyan and Fu Bi

562
00:33:37,380 --> 00:33:38,660
were holding important posts.

563
00:33:39,900 --> 00:33:41,860
Xia Song was demoted and banished
from the Capital.

564
00:33:43,580 --> 00:33:44,380
You wrote,

565
00:33:46,100 --> 00:33:51,100
Fan Zhongyan and Fu Bi are great officials.

566
00:33:52,180 --> 00:33:56,580
They dare to carry out the reform.

567
00:33:58,180 --> 00:34:02,140
Using wise men is like pulling up the weeds.

568
00:34:02,300 --> 00:34:06,940
Dismissing villains is like cutting chicken feet.

569
00:34:09,580 --> 00:34:14,780
So far, Fan Zhongyan and Fu Bi

570
00:34:20,860 --> 00:34:22,180
have left the Capital.

571
00:34:25,460 --> 00:34:27,380
But Xia Song is back.

572
00:34:40,260 --> 00:34:41,380
Even if I have to be demoted,

573
00:34:43,580 --> 00:34:44,860
punished

574
00:34:47,540 --> 00:34:49,260
or even killed,

575
00:34:50,780 --> 00:34:55,260
I’ll complain for Xiwen and Yanguo,

576
00:34:57,780 --> 00:34:59,700
and I’ll vindicate you.

577
00:35:01,300 --> 00:35:02,180
By then,

578
00:35:03,460 --> 00:35:04,620
I will come back

579
00:35:06,540 --> 00:35:07,500
and drink a toast to you.

580
00:35:18,940 --> 00:35:19,980
From Ouyang Xiu again?

581
00:35:20,820 --> 00:35:21,460
Yes.

582
00:35:25,860 --> 00:35:27,060
One proposal per day.

583
00:35:27,780 --> 00:35:29,460
I’ll see when he will stop.

584
00:35:34,140 --> 00:35:35,820
= East Gate =

585
00:35:35,820 --> 00:35:38,140
Ouyang Xiu submits a long proposal every day,

586
00:35:38,700 --> 00:35:40,660
complaining for Fan Zhongyan and Fu Bi

587
00:35:40,860 --> 00:35:42,380
and trying to vindicate Shi Jie.

588
00:35:43,260 --> 00:35:45,260
Also, he complains about His Majesty

589
00:35:45,820 --> 00:35:47,300
for promoting his incompetent uncle.

590
00:35:47,660 --> 00:35:49,660
What should the Cabinet do?

591
00:35:52,220 --> 00:35:54,020
His Majesty didn’t review the proposals.

592
00:35:54,340 --> 00:35:55,940
Yan Shu replied nothing, either.

593
00:35:56,540 --> 00:35:57,940
The proposals are laid aside,

594
00:35:58,060 --> 00:35:59,220
let them be.

595
00:36:00,900 --> 00:36:02,540
His Majesty always admires

596
00:36:02,540 --> 00:36:05,020
Fan Zhongyan and Ouyang Xiu for their talents.

597
00:36:05,980 --> 00:36:06,940
As for Mr. Yan,

598
00:36:07,020 --> 00:36:08,100
you know...

599
00:36:09,300 --> 00:36:09,780
Hya.

600
00:36:11,300 --> 00:36:12,820
Mr. Yan seems to be fair.

601
00:36:13,460 --> 00:36:17,260
But Fu Bi is his son-in-law, anyway.

602
00:36:19,060 --> 00:36:20,340
If the problem remains unsolved...

603
00:36:20,340 --> 00:36:21,780
With Yan Shu and Han Qi,

604
00:36:22,220 --> 00:36:24,100
His Majesty might be convinced by Ouyang Xiu

605
00:36:24,780 --> 00:36:26,740
and the reform might start again.

606
00:36:29,580 --> 00:36:30,820
Ouyang Xiu and Fan Zhongyan

607
00:36:30,820 --> 00:36:32,860
directly said I was evil.

608
00:36:33,540 --> 00:36:34,740
They also

609
00:36:35,860 --> 00:36:37,740
criticize you.

610
00:36:39,300 --> 00:36:41,180
Ouyang Xiu claims to be a gentleman.

611
00:36:41,420 --> 00:36:42,540
But he doesn’t behave well.

612
00:36:43,540 --> 00:36:46,380
Censor Qian Mingyi told me

613
00:36:47,220 --> 00:36:50,540
Ouyang Xiu often visited brothels
when he was young.

614
00:36:51,100 --> 00:36:52,460
Instead of feeling ashamed,

615
00:36:52,460 --> 00:36:54,260
he even wrote erotic poems for singing.

616
00:36:56,860 --> 00:36:59,700
There’s something we don’t take charge of.

617
00:37:00,500 --> 00:37:03,220
Mr. Jia, please kindly check it.

618
00:37:05,340 --> 00:37:06,100
What is it?

619
00:37:07,660 --> 00:37:08,900
One month ago,

620
00:37:09,060 --> 00:37:10,380
Ouyang Xiu’s niece

621
00:37:10,380 --> 00:37:11,780
was accused of fornicating with a servant

622
00:37:11,980 --> 00:37:14,340
in Kaifeng Municipal Government

623
00:37:14,340 --> 00:37:15,380
and was detained for trial.

624
00:37:17,460 --> 00:37:19,140
She confessed it.

625
00:37:20,140 --> 00:37:21,460
But Ouyang Xiu’s family

626
00:37:22,100 --> 00:37:25,540
bribed the government for the withdrawal.

627
00:37:30,100 --> 00:37:31,980
He has such a scandal at home.

628
00:37:32,620 --> 00:37:33,900
In the imperial court,

629
00:37:33,900 --> 00:37:36,300
it’s not surprised

630
00:37:36,300 --> 00:37:38,060
when he’s accused of indiscretion.

631
00:37:39,460 --> 00:37:43,380
He’s afraid that he’ll be embarrassed

632
00:37:43,460 --> 00:37:44,980
if it goes around.

633
00:37:46,340 --> 00:37:49,900
Maybe he has used money

634
00:37:50,820 --> 00:37:51,900
to persuade his niece’s husband.

635
00:37:53,900 --> 00:37:55,500
That’s why

636
00:37:55,500 --> 00:37:56,580
I’m telling you about it.

637
00:37:57,060 --> 00:37:59,060
You should check carefully on that.

638
00:37:59,580 --> 00:38:01,620
Don’t omit

639
00:38:02,140 --> 00:38:04,140
any scandal of Ouyang Xiu’s family.

640
00:38:08,820 --> 00:38:09,380
Hya.

641
00:38:14,420 --> 00:38:16,180
In the Capital and neighboring areas,

642
00:38:16,180 --> 00:38:18,300
the pestilence has been eliminated.

643
00:38:19,580 --> 00:38:23,660
I, Ouyang Xiu,
demand a conversation with Your Majesty.

644
00:38:28,020 --> 00:38:29,300
Go tell Ouyang Xiu

645
00:38:30,380 --> 00:38:32,820
I’m discussing with ministers today

646
00:38:32,820 --> 00:38:33,780
and he can leave.

647
00:38:35,860 --> 00:38:36,740
In this year’s pestilence,

648
00:38:37,060 --> 00:38:39,620
we had timely precautions and treatment.

649
00:38:40,100 --> 00:38:41,100
Fewer people were sick

650
00:38:41,100 --> 00:38:42,660
than those in the previous pestilences.

651
00:38:42,660 --> 00:38:43,340
Your Majesty.

652
00:38:44,180 --> 00:38:45,460
Half a month ago, with the determination to die,

653
00:38:45,980 --> 00:38:48,460
I submitted a proposal

654
00:38:49,060 --> 00:38:51,220
with heartbroken complaints.

655
00:38:51,260 --> 00:38:53,380
I only want you to review it.

656
00:38:54,180 --> 00:38:55,300
If you refute my proposal

657
00:38:55,660 --> 00:38:57,740
in my face

658
00:38:57,900 --> 00:38:59,900
and resolve my doubts,

659
00:39:00,180 --> 00:39:03,940
I won’t regret even if I’m executed immediately.

660
00:39:06,540 --> 00:39:07,740
The determination to die?

661
00:39:09,260 --> 00:39:10,620
Be executed?

662
00:39:15,740 --> 00:39:17,060
Go on, Han Qi.

663
00:39:19,780 --> 00:39:20,900
- Sick... - Your Majesty.

664
00:39:21,780 --> 00:39:25,220
Shi Jie has been dead for nearly a month.

665
00:39:26,220 --> 00:39:28,700
When I was sad,

666
00:39:29,300 --> 00:39:30,860
I compiled the articles he wrote before he died.

667
00:39:31,500 --> 00:39:34,820
I saw Ode to Imperial Virtue

668
00:39:34,940 --> 00:39:36,540
and I read it again and again.

669
00:39:37,220 --> 00:39:40,460
My ancestors left me the nation.

670
00:39:40,980 --> 00:39:44,860
In case I may lose it, I rely on ministers.

671
00:39:46,060 --> 00:39:48,020
I feel so pathetic and confused.

672
00:39:48,780 --> 00:39:52,220
Your Majesty, to protect ancestral properties,

673
00:39:52,980 --> 00:39:57,420
you promote honest officials
Fan Zhongyan and Fu Bi.

674
00:39:57,980 --> 00:40:00,340
You trust them and use them.

675
00:40:01,020 --> 00:40:04,820
Fan Zhongyan is made the Consultant,

676
00:40:04,820 --> 00:40:06,340
to defend my reputation.

677
00:40:06,700 --> 00:40:09,740
He helps me out, regardless of slanders.

678
00:40:10,300 --> 00:40:13,620
I want to stop Xixia from invading us.

679
00:40:14,860 --> 00:40:18,020
Fu Bi then works for years

680
00:40:18,500 --> 00:40:22,180
devoting himself to guarding the border.

681
00:40:22,460 --> 00:40:23,780
He isn’t scared even when Khitan betrays us.

682
00:40:25,300 --> 00:40:30,300
He risks his life on the border.

683
00:40:31,940 --> 00:40:35,500
Your Majesty, may I ask you?

684
00:40:36,780 --> 00:40:40,220
Did Shi Jie make up anything in his ode?

685
00:40:41,140 --> 00:40:44,540
Are Fan and Fu truly guilty?

686
00:40:46,180 --> 00:40:49,700
If they are, why don’t you tell the public?

687
00:40:50,300 --> 00:40:51,260
If they aren’t,

688
00:40:52,380 --> 00:40:55,540
why did they resign and leave the Capital?

689
00:41:02,940 --> 00:41:04,820
Ouyang Xiu is making such noise

690
00:41:05,580 --> 00:41:07,700
that I can’t focus on the discussion.

691
00:41:09,220 --> 00:41:10,100
We’ll discuss about it some other day.

692
00:41:11,260 --> 00:41:13,460
Your Majesty, have you changed your mind

693
00:41:13,620 --> 00:41:17,420
when you opened the Hall of Articles,

694
00:41:18,060 --> 00:41:19,060
gave Fan Zhongyan the paper and writing brush

695
00:41:19,220 --> 00:41:21,780
and asked him to write down ten orders?

696
00:41:22,300 --> 00:41:25,300
Have you lost your resolution

697
00:41:25,540 --> 00:41:27,580
to promote good officials and fire evil ones?

698
00:41:28,580 --> 00:41:33,740
That’s why loyal officials are away or aggrieved.

699
00:41:34,220 --> 00:41:36,020
Evil officials come back, instead!

700
00:41:36,980 --> 00:41:41,980
You promote mediocre relatives to important posts.

701
00:41:45,500 --> 00:41:47,580
Promote mediocre relatives to important posts!

702
00:41:48,580 --> 00:41:49,500
He is condemning me!

703
00:41:50,020 --> 00:41:51,260
He thinks my relatives are mediocre

704
00:41:51,260 --> 00:41:52,100
and I am fatuous!

705
00:41:52,780 --> 00:41:54,460
Fine! Fine!

706
00:41:55,820 --> 00:41:56,700
Today...

707
00:41:56,700 --> 00:41:57,460
Your Majesty.

708
00:42:00,060 --> 00:42:02,140
Ouyang Xiu is always honest and impulsive.

709
00:42:02,260 --> 00:42:04,060
He’s too sad when Shi Jie was framed up

710
00:42:04,420 --> 00:42:05,460
and died with grievance.

711
00:42:05,900 --> 00:42:06,980
He holds extreme view then.

712
00:42:07,780 --> 00:42:08,700
Your Majesty,

713
00:42:09,300 --> 00:42:11,140
please show some mercy on him

714
00:42:11,460 --> 00:42:12,500
considering his simple mind

715
00:42:15,500 --> 00:42:16,660
and his loyalty.

716
00:42:23,020 --> 00:42:23,940
Get Ouyang Xiu in.

717
00:42:25,740 --> 00:42:26,900
Since he insists on having a debate,

718
00:42:28,660 --> 00:42:31,620
I’ll let you do it in the hall.

719
00:42:42,180 --> 00:42:51,820
♪ Loved you a gentleman yet got abandoned ♪

720
00:42:53,180 --> 00:43:01,500
♪ Peach blossoms color the city ♪

721
00:43:04,340 --> 00:43:09,060
♪ Spring breeze purified dusty memories ♪

722
00:43:10,060 --> 00:43:14,220
♪ The gate of the vast palace opens ♪

723
00:43:15,660 --> 00:43:21,140
♪ Bid farewell with wine after the glory ends ♪

724
00:43:21,140 --> 00:43:25,900
♪ Outside the city a beautiful world unveils ♪

725
00:43:29,580 --> 00:43:35,220
♪ Long-standing distance doesn’t alienate us ♪

726
00:43:35,220 --> 00:43:40,140
♪ Keep you company behind the gate ♪

727
00:43:40,620 --> 00:43:46,380
♪ Four seasons come and go ♪

728
00:43:46,380 --> 00:43:51,460
♪ We only have each other in this cage ♪

729
00:43:51,900 --> 00:43:56,820
♪ Wish to fly freely in the next life ♪

730
00:43:57,460 --> 00:44:02,300
♪ Willows turn green flowers red ♪

731
00:44:02,980 --> 00:44:08,140
♪ Sing aloud with wine ♪

732
00:44:08,660 --> 00:44:13,700
♪ Hold your hands and go home together ♪

733
00:44:14,220 --> 00:44:18,300
♪ Be a pair of swallows in the next life ♪

734
00:44:19,780 --> 00:44:24,420
♪ Build the nest and protect the nestlings ♪

735
00:44:25,420 --> 00:44:30,580
♪ The howling wind ♪

736
00:44:30,940 --> 00:44:35,020
♪ Woke me up from the dream ♪

737
00:44:36,500 --> 00:44:41,420
♪ Be a pair of swallows in the next life ♪

738
00:44:42,100 --> 00:44:47,300
♪ Build the nest and protect the nestlings ♪

739
00:44:47,740 --> 00:44:53,020
♪ The howling wind ♪

740
00:44:53,300 --> 00:44:58,180
♪ Woke me up from the dream ♪

741
00:44:58,780 --> 00:45:05,500
♪ Life is long yet joy is little ♪
